# Title
Emergency Order for the Protection of the Greater Sage-Grouse


# ID
SOR-2013-202

# URL
http://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/regulations/SOR-2013-202/FullText.html


# Summary
Non-application Paragraphs (1)(a) to (f) do not apply either inside or within 100 m of a residential building that exists on the date of the coming into force of this Order; a building that is used for the purposes of an agricultural operation if it exists on the date of the coming into force of this Order; a shelter that is used for the purposes of an agricultural operation if it remains at the same place where it was located on the date of the coming into force of this Order; or a structure or machine that is used to feed, handle, treat or provide water to grazing animals if it is used at the same place where it was used before the coming into force of this Order.
Non-application Subsection (1) does not apply either inside or within 100 m of a residential building that exists on the date of the coming into force of this Order; a building that is used for the purposes of an agricultural operation if it exists on the date of the coming into force of this Order; a shelter that is used for the purposes of an agricultural operation if it remains at the same place where it was located on the date of the coming into force of this Order; or a structure or machine that is used to feed, handle, treat or provide water to grazing animals if it is used at the same place where it was used before the coming into force of this Order.
